# Suggested Readings

Note: Readings with an asterisk in front of them are ones we have read and enjoyed.

*Hewlett, Sylvia Ann (2013). Forget a Mentor, Find a Sponsor: The New Way to Fast-Track Your Career. Cambridge, MA: Harvard Business Press.

Hogan, Kevin (1999). Talk Your Way to the Top: Communication Secrets to Change Your Life. Gretna, LA: Pelican Publishing Company.

Lerner, Helene (2015). The Confidence Myth: Why Women undervalue their skills, and how to get over it. Oakland, California : Berrett-Koehler Publishers, Inc.

Monarth, Harrison (2009). Executive Presence: The Art of Commanding Respect Like a CEO. New York, NY: McGraw-Hill.


